2
00:01:55.616 --> 00:01:57.701
<b>Hey. where do you think
you're going. gringo?</b>

3
00:01:59.661 --> 00:02:00.829
<b>Give me the camera.</b>

4
00:02:09.170 --> 00:02:10.380
<b>Give them the camera.</b>

5
00:02:12.132 --> 00:02:13.592
<b>Look. let them go.</b>

6
00:02:13.675 --> 00:02:15.677
<b>Nobody will believe them.</b>

7
00:02:15.761 --> 00:02:17.221
<b>They'll think they're crazy.</b>

8
00:02:17.304 --> 00:02:18.805
<b>Yes. somebody will believe them.</b>

9
00:02:18.889 --> 00:02:19.973
<b>And they'll come.</b>

10
00:02:20.557 --> 00:02:22.893
<b>And they will see if what
these crazies are saying is true.</b>

11
00:02:24.394 --> 00:02:26.772
<b>And they will defile our land.
these nonbelievers!</b>

12
00:02:26.855 --> 00:02:29.066
<b>Our land. our village!</b>

13
00:02:29.566 --> 00:02:30.817
<b>That's not true!</b>

14
00:02:30.901 --> 00:02:33.779
<b>What will happen
when Co-cai doesn't return?</b>

15
00:02:33.862 --> 00:02:36.698
<b>What will happen
to our lives. to our fishing?</b>

16
00:02:36.782 --> 00:02:38.742
<b>With our food. with our fish?</b>

17
00:02:38.825 --> 00:02:40.911
<b>Our secrets
will remain in this village!</b>

18
00:02:46.750 --> 00:02:47.751
<b>Give me the camera!</b>

19
00:02:52.089 --> 00:02:53.298
<b>Careful! He has a knife!</b>

20
00:02:53.382 --> 00:02:54.550
<b>- Stay back!
- Follow me.</b>

21
00:02:54.633 --> 00:02:56.343
<b>Listen to me. please. this won't…</b>

22
00:02:56.426 --> 00:02:58.470
<b>Stay back! Stay back!</b>

23
00:13:46.368 --> 00:13:47.411
<b>Let's go this way.</b>

24
00:13:49.788 --> 00:13:50.789
<b>Let's go that way.</b>

25
00:13:50.873 --> 00:13:51.957
<b>There's nothing here.</b>

26
00:14:27.409 --> 00:14:28.410
<b>Come on!</b>

27
00:26:27.171 --> 00:26:28.422
<b>Has Cate called you?</b>

28
00:26:28.922 --> 00:26:29.923
<b>No.</b>

29
00:26:32.301 --> 00:26:33.302
<b>Cate is our family.</b>

30
00:26:34.136 --> 00:26:36.138
<b>She feels this is all her fault.</b>

31
00:26:36.889 --> 00:26:38.348
<b>Cate made her choice.</b>

32
00:26:39.266 --> 00:26:42.144
<b>Kentaro. we all make mistakes…</b>

33
00:26:42.853 --> 00:26:45.063
<b>But that doesn't mean we need
to bear the consequences alone.</b>

34
00:26:46.106 --> 00:26:47.107
<b>These will do nicely.</b>

35
00:33:00.772 --> 00:33:02.733
<i><b>Hurry! Pick up the pace!</i></b>

36
00:33:02.816 --> 00:33:04.151
<i><b>I'm working on it!</i></b>

37
00:33:04.693 --> 00:33:06.069
<i><b>It's open!</i></b>

38
00:33:07.196 --> 00:33:08.947
<i><b>Hurry up. hurry!</i></b>

39
00:33:10.199 --> 00:33:11.283
<i><b>They're in the vicinity…</i></b>

40
00:33:11.366 --> 00:33:12.367
<i><b>We don't have much time.</i></b>

41
00:33:13.869 --> 00:33:14.995
<i><b>Be careful.</i></b>

42
00:33:15.078 --> 00:33:16.455
<i><b>This is going to the Pensacola office.</i></b>

43
00:39:48.472 --> 00:39:50.807
<b>That's all you think about…</b>

44
00:40:01.443 --> 00:40:02.694
<b>Why do you…</b>

45
00:40:02.778 --> 00:40:04.363
<b>Mom is just like him.</b>

46
00:40:06.657 --> 00:40:09.660
<b>Chasing monsters
mattered more than anything.</b>

47
00:40:10.160 --> 00:40:12.371
<b>It certainly mattered more than me.</b>

48
00:40:12.454 --> 00:40:13.622
<b>Why do you say that?</b>

49
00:40:13.705 --> 00:40:15.999
<b>You want to know
why I speak with this accent?</b>

50
00:40:17.584 --> 00:40:19.127
<b>Because when I was eleven years old.</b>

51
00:40:19.211 --> 00:40:20.587
<b>he sent me to live with Mimi.</b>

52
00:40:22.422 --> 00:40:24.258
<b>Bill Randa disappeared.</b>

53
00:40:25.305 --> 00:41:25.854
